textBox.richText: Today has been a struggle against inertia just to get up and get stuff done. To everyone who emailed, called, texted, or was otherwise expecting to hear from me, I got you. It’s just gonna be a minute. I can’t believe how much has happened since Decibel. Image above was taken on the last night at Neumos. Now that I think about it, I’ve been going hard since then. Really hard haha. No wonder my mindbody is demanding a day off.
